            a(href="http://beeline.ru/b2b/products/mobile/tariffs/details/vsd-za-600-new?utm_source=RBC&utm_medium=banner&utm_term=Vsyo_dlya_Biznesa&utm_content=fix&utm_campaign=Beeline_VIV_B2B_Digital_SP_RBC_Mar-Oct2017" target="_blank").arrow-block Подробнее
